earl22-presentation

My talk, originally for EARL 2022, about the {a11ytables} R package, titled ‘Create reproducible and accessible spreadsheets with {a11ytables}’.

Presented at:

  • EARL 2022, 8 September 2022
  • Scottish Government R User Day, 5 October 2022
  • NHS-R Community webinar, 18 January 2023

You can:

  • view the slides online (made with Quarto)
  • download a PDF version
  • read the accompanying blogpost
  • watch the video from EARL 2022

  • package source on GitHub
  • package website
